Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不要一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司还在我的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 我在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪里都不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.92,0:00:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我开动啰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:00:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会不会觉得我做得比以前好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是每天积累的成果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可是认真做就能做好的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.17,0:01:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.64,0:01:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}味道怎么样
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂喂 司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你现在是不是非常的想要去看电影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是这样想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以把这个拿好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是为什么突然给我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克很少会给我礼物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是因为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满来拜托我帮她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我才
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啦你给我收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟艾拉两个人去开心一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话先说在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只是很偶然地拿到了票
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我可是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只好把票让给很闲的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的只是这样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:03:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总之谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}噢 司君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这些你不介意的话就收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}游览地旅馆的目录
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要好好地利用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我拿到了平时常去的饭店的招待券
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}店里有着装规定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我替你们准备了正装
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是餐时表演的票和加油用品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}粉丝俱乐部的特典里多放了两份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愿意的话就拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你随时都可以开走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}停车场的地址在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么 你没有驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事没事有自动驾驶功能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉呢 司君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我每个月的零用钱都好紧张的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我只能给你这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 机会难得 明天要休个假一起去逛逛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是像梦一般的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想做的事还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好奇心真强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}激情退却了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要好好的体验人生才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不然就太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只要能够独占你动人的笑容就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要这样我就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一次看电影觉得怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到现在还不能平静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:06:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才一直握着我的手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是因为在黑暗的地方就担心司会不会忽然不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感到很不安…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给你添麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的手你再怎么握都没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 司 我想试试电影里的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道是膝枕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的膝盖可以用的…所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…那就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司的头发有点刺人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}超级害羞就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}错误 没有听清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 错误什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实是听清楚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我没听到哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我最近害怕晚上睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会去想象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会不会再也醒不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会不会再也见不到司了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是像这样和司在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那种感觉就咻的消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可以随时来依靠我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:08:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从大家那里感觉到超级强的「明天休息吧」的气场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司想要去玩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}表情很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然这样的每一天都很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是这样下去身体会迟钝的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果…在迎接最后一天之前就不能动了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就好讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 不可能有那种事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过 一不小心就开始胡思乱想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那样的话…果然还是像平常那样度过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天这样的日子偶尔过一过就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}数据上没有什么显眼的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太慢了 迟到10分钟了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}工作太忙了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道今天也来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 那俩人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有必要这么频繁的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也好 对本人来说能安抚一下情绪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算如此 也没必要休息日也过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看到他们两个人就想哭了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 过来一下好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正好我也有事情想问香月姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}希望你把下一个工作交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和艾拉负责的变成只有莎拉小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什… 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉的回收同意书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}由你来签名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你暂时集中关注艾拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:10:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}德国洋甘菊是一年生的草本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直长着叶子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}种子落下来同时会长出新的芽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放置不管的话会长一大片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有不好的 最好是摘下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这边的百里香怕热小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反过来迷迭香很耐热
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是如果不整理的话叶子会太繁茂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下面会枯掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夏天应该收获一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉很了解药草呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}研究了很久吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚开始培育的时候有很多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且只要大家说我泡的茶好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就觉得我能在这里待着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还想种些别的看看呢
Comment: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这货在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为现在只有我和艾拉的工作很轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就想着有没有什么其他可做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就让艾拉教我这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最近好像找到窍门了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「找到窍门了」个头啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我才受不了外行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正好趁这个机会跟你说明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么不去休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你倒是稍微看一下气氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「咦」个头啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起来公司上班 你应该多花些时间来陪艾拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算你们不来上班大家也不会抱怨的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们不能休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然满和大家说的 我们很感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我和艾拉两个人做出了决定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就和平常一样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我希望大家能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满 是你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也是对他们一直放心不下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:13:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你 满
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我也想象珍惜和司的时间一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}珍惜在这里度过的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算了 随便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了 你们也别看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快回去工作 别偷懒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 待会还有约会要去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小艾拉 能再帮我倒杯茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 现在有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个的签名 由我来签
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我希望司来签
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:14:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的脑中有时会闪现出一些想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们就这样逃到远方会怎样之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就在想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}该怎样不告诉任何人然后离开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给你留下了痛苦的回忆了呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}水柿司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天就是莎拉小姐的回收日了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们两个负责的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这就是最后一件了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}是的 您说的我都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}但是让我们什么都不做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}也未免太说不过去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}是是 那个…那个…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那两个人已经走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}请您通融一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还剩下一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\fad(320,50)\c&H49465B&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(649,263)}有一件讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}莎拉小姐的回收已经完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果有兴趣的话就回办公室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们的工作也就全部告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:18:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们准备为你们开个小小的慰问会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然也不用勉强非要来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管怎样先优先处理你们自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算你们不来 我们也会HIGH起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然这样说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.12,0:18:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欢迎回来～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欢迎～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们已经开始了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天的主角出现啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在公司里喝酒真的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事 没事～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在这里的全员都已经把工作提前完成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然康孝你好像只是睡了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了腾出今天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家可是拚命提前完成了工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为此大家上周都过得非常忙碌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管怎么说 现在已经是非工作时间啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我允许你们饮酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不 这是我允许的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可是为了得到许可 卑躬屈膝地求了部长好久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要老命了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你做的很好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 两位请拿好这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的 全员注意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么长时间以来 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么 干杯啰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.45,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(251,142)\fsp0}香月就交给我吧。\N\N康斯坦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.45,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(337,335)}辛苦了。暂时忘掉工作，\N先考虑自己的幸福吧，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.45,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(320,443)}啊，不介意的话，什么时候\N来我房间里玩都可以哟？\N满
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.45,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(460,570)}谢谢你总是泡茶给我们。\N非常好喝唷。\N山野边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.45,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(298,667)}再见啰～\N塞克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.45,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs30\c&H393939&\pos(711,137)}辛苦啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.45,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(877,142)}害羞了（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.45,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\fs30\c&H393939&\3c&HFAFCFC&\pos(782,433)}艾拉 辛苦啦~！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.45,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an7\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(701,600)}艾拉酱LOVE\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h海松绘瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.45,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(1222,201)}第一终端服务课的友情永远不灭！\N土器连
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.45,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(1250,341)}从现在开始尽情对喜欢的男生撒娇吧。\N那样的任性会被允许的。\N康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.45,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(1235,470)}与你一起共事是非常值得骄傲的一件事。\N雪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.45,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(1238,615)}单元测验房会一直为你保留着的。\N右次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘿～嘿～加油～加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘿～嘿～加油～加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉好像很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没想到你们真的回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}发来信息的就是满吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然是那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然嘴上这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说要开这个会的就是满啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 为什么每次都要戳穿我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}来 接着喝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么啊 反正我早就知道司是个需要别人照顾的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你笑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:21:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你才是在笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才没在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}笑啦 笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克你也这样
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}累了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 好像有一点闹过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事啦 没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得 虽然发生了许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是能在那里工作真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能遇到大家 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在开心的 愉快的事太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多到日记里都写不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这些都是托司的福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.02,0:21:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可以问个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天你对莎拉小姐说了些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:21:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:22:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前 每次回收的最后你都一定会那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我之前就很在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会想你都说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「愿你终将与重要的人再次相会」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
